---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`About - ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="About Hayley Feng" />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
			<div class="text-xs text-neutral-600 light:text-neutral-400 mb-6">
				<span class="text-green-400 light:text-green-600">hayley@dev</span>:<span class="text-cyan-400 light:text-cyan-600">~</span>$ cat about.md
			</div>

			<div class="prose">
				<h1 class="!text-xl !mb-6">About</h1>

				<p>
					Hi. I'm <strong>Hayley Feng</strong>, a full-stack developer who enjoys building products that work well and code that reads well.
				</p>

				<h2>Stack</h2>

				<ul>
					<li><strong>Backend</strong> &mdash; Python, FastAPI, PostgreSQL</li>
					<li><strong>Frontend</strong> &mdash; React, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS</li>
					<li><strong>Exploring</strong> &mdash; LLMs, AI Agents, Rust</li>
					<li><strong>Infra</strong> &mdash; Docker, GitHub Actions, Vercel</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>Why This Blog</h2>

				<p>
					Writing is thinking. I use this space to document what I learn, break down problems I've solved, and occasionally rant about developer tooling. If something here saves you 30 minutes of debugging, it was worth writing.
				</p>

				<h2>Contact</h2>

				<p>
					Find me on <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank">GitHub</a>. Open to conversations about tech, open source, and collaboration.
				</p>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
